  {
    "id": "session-11-sand-people-get-in-all-the-crevices_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "Session 11 - Sand People Get In All the Crevices",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "2",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-11-sand-people-get-in-all-the-crevices_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The kNight Watch pressed deeper into the Jagged Waste Crags to locate the Radiant Eye cult outpost and secure the lost celestial instrument. They defeated a band of Mahruudian Raiders in a fierce running battle across the cliffs, claiming two kahlbits as new mounts along with supplies and a potion of fire breath. Seraphine examined the raiders' strange sun-sensitive bodies before the party fought and killed two packs of dire wolves that had been feeding on humanoids. They tracked the wolves to a series of terraced caves, avoided a hidden pit trap under a blood-soaked tapestry at the entrance, and the session ended with the group standing in a suspicious cave.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "3",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
