    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-4-i-can-t-even-take-a_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "Session 4 - I Can't Even Take A ...",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "30",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-4-i-can-t-even-take-a_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party set out to track down the escaped bandits and the freed prisoner before they could disappear beyond Hesfal's reach. Following the trail into dense wilderness, they uncovered signs of deception, fought through hostile terrain, and survived a violent encounter with an owlbear and a swarm of stirges that nearly cost them their mounts. Their pursuit paid off with the discovery of a hidden cache and the bandits' horses, confirming they were closing in. The session ended with the party setting an ambush and holding their ground as the sound of someone approaching broke the silence.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "31",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-4-i-can-t-even-take-a_recording_1",
    "type": "media-player",
    "props": {
      "title": "Session 04 Recording",
      "src": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Cj2mOZDo4XhLe4qx6ClcHI-hATCzC9dR/view?usp=drive_link",
      "mediaType": "auto",
      "caption": "",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "32",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "2",
      "displayMode": "image-button",
      "image": "/images/dragon-ears.png"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-3-chase-the-runners_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "Session 3 - Chase the Runners",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "34",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-3-chase-the-runners_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party focused on containing the fallout from the coordinated attacks in Hesfal and preventing the perpetrators from escaping justice. They attempted to stop the fleeing criminals using quick thinking and improvised tools, but the escape only partially failed, leaving unanswered questions and wounded allies in its wake. As the town struggled to regain order, the group uncovered troubling signs that the robbery, jailbreak, and recent murder were connected. By morning, they committed to pursuing the runners beyond Hesfal, gathering evidence, securing mounts, and preparing to take the hunt onto the road.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "35",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-3-chase-the-runners_recording_1",
    "type": "media-player",
    "props": {
      "title": "Session 03 Recording",
      "src": "https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mHUEPXACaki6v2rdXhazP8-cBt9EGt-J/view?usp=drive_link",
      "mediaType": "auto",
      "caption": "",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "36",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "2",
      "displayMode": "image-button",
      "image": "/images/dragon-ears.png"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-2-a-pocket-prism_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "Session 2 - A Pocket Prism",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "38",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-2-a-pocket-prism_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party tried to enjoy a brief return to normalcy as Hesfal filled with travelers ahead of the Salvus festival, while keeping a wary eye on rumors of violence and unrest. What began as music, conversation, and curiosity about strange newcomers quickly turned dangerous when a coordinated tavern robbery erupted around them. The group stepped in to protect civilians and stop the attackers, only to discover the violence was part of something larger when the Town Ward was breached and prisoners were freed. By the end of the night, the party found themselves split across multiple threats, realizing that the chaos in Hesfal was organized, deliberate, and far from over.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "39",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-2-a-pocket-prism_recording_1",
