    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-1-it-s-aeon_title",
    "type": "header",
    "props": {
      "title": "Session 1 - It's Aeon",
      "color": "gold",
      "size": "md",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "42",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "session-1-it-s-aeon_summary",
    "type": "text",
    "props": {
      "content": "The party was united by circumstance, curiosity, and quiet personal searching as they each arrived in Hesfal on the eve of the Salvus festival. Individually, they sought rest, healing, faith, or simple opportunity, crossing paths in temples, taverns, and trading halls while sharing fragments of their pasts. Conversations revealed lingering scars from the Awakening, unresolved devotions to distant gods, and hints of deeper mysteries tying some of them together. By session's end, chance encounters gave way to recognition and shared history, just as the arrival of the final Salvus caravan signaled that Hesfal was about to become crowded, tense, and ripe for whatever fate was drawing them together.",
      "col": "1",
      "row": "43",
      "colSpan": "1",
      "rowSpan": "1"
    }
